- trestare che invii email
- caricare file csv con email e compleanni in formato -> salvarli in db
- inviare gli auguri a quelli che compiono gli anni quando digiti invio
- automatizzare l'invio degli auguri

Implementa architettura esagonale:
src/
├── application/
│ ├── BirthdayService.ts
├── domain/
│ ├── Employee.ts
│ ├── EmployeeRepository.ts
│ ├── EmailService.ts
├── infrastructure/
│ ├── FlatFileEmployeeRepository.ts
│ ├── MockEmailService.ts
├── index.ts

Si potrebbe fare dentro a src/models?

The goal of this exercise is to come up with a solution that is

Testable; we should be able to test the internal application logic with no need to ever send a real email.
Flexible: we anticipate that the data source in the future could change from a flat file to a relational database, or perhaps a web service. We also anticipate that the email service could soon be replaced with a service that sends greetings through Facebook or some other social network.
Well-designed: separate clearly the business logic from the infrastructure
